Hey bro, if you are having issue on the definition not showing in your webpage try to remove the curly braces from you mapping code or just copy paste this code. 

meanings.map((mean) =>
          mean.meanings.map((item) =>
            item.definitions.map((def) => (
              <div
                className="singleMean"
                style={{ backgroundColor: 'white', color: 'black' }}
              >
                <b>{def.definition}</b>
              </div>
            ))
          )
        )
